name: Invisible Dudes #1 | Sherlock Tez
description: Invisible Dudes are invisible. Sherlock Tez is the genius sleuth from Tezland Yard, hellbent on thwarting the devious plans of his arch nemesis, criminal mastermind Tezriarty... With the help of his trusty sidekick Tezland Moore, Sherlock Tez will use his expert detective skills to protect the citizens of Tezland Yard from Tezriarty's criminal activities. Invisible Dudes are created by @clipdad_
